{"tid":1276808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳沛然：醫警系統現沒實線相連","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:02:03.000Z","uid":51469,"like":7,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6a443bd779d32078d345964083dd7476432592","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】立法會醫學界議員陳沛然周三（19日）發表〈醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統是相連的〉網誌，質疑警方的重大事件調查及災難支援工作系統（MIIDSS）或與醫管局電腦系統相連。醫管局行政總裁梁栢賢昨回應，已澄清醫管局系統與警方的MIIDSS沒聯繫，很多市民信了陳沛然的質疑，陳有責任澄清，但未有澄清，「如果他知道這方面不真確，希望他能幫忙，澄清早前的懷疑不正確」。<br />\n<br />\n梁栢賢續表示歡迎對醫管局提出意見，又呼籲「如有懷疑，希望先給我們機會澄清和解釋，如一開始就在網絡上用這方法做，香港的信任較低迷，若將不好的信息散播了，到我們解釋時可能已經太遲」。<br />\n<br />\n陳沛然昨日再發表〈我們必需盡快堵塞洩露病人資料漏洞〉網誌回應，提及醫管局已澄清現在醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統，並沒有直接用實體線相連。他又稱，「經過激烈討論後，期望能成功堵塞將來經醫護同事及經電腦系統，泄露病人私隱予警方的可能」。至於警方在急症室獲得資訊，他認為醫管局應繼續直接跟警務處對話，也促請醫管局好好管理醫院範圍，「阻止作出妨擾事件的人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561055519296/%E6%A2%81%E6%A0%A2%E8%B3%A2%E4%BF%83%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E9%99%B3%E6%B2%9B%E7%84%B6-%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%8F%BE%E6%B2%92%E5%AF%A6%E7%B7%9A%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561055519296%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B2%259B%25E7%2584%25B6-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2580%25A3&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=9b558172\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190621%2Fs00001%2F1561055519296%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25B2%259B%25E7%2584%25B6-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25B2%2592%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2580%25A3&h=4cc1d945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190621/s00001/1561055519296/%E6%A2%81%E6%A0%A2%E8%B3%A2%E4%BF%83%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E9%99%B3%E6%B2%9B%E7%84%B6-%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%8F%BE%E6%B2%92%E5%AF%A6%E7%B7%9A%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n原來咁多人唔知陳沛然一早收皮認左HA冇過料俾警察,<br />\n希望大家屌HA同時認清一下事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲講緊有人即時抄資料走人，你做乜撚？"},{"pid":"d386a218c413df1f240232d6184407ae5392f87b","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲講緊有人即時抄資料走人，你做乜撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"你抄俾我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳沛然當日係話HA乜架?<br />\n你又唔睇下DR RAY點認為?佢做開急症喎"},{"pid":"62f5711c88fe00389534f73ba8ff193f11aff72e","tid":1276808,"uid":60615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"你老母而家係打開database俾驚察任睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dda41f566c49cbc07bd49c48df549328bca25e3","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"62f5711c88fe00389534f73ba8ff193f11aff72e","tid":1276808,"uid":60615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"你老母而家係打開database俾驚察任睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"一直都收到讀者的疑問，我還是忍不住要改一改，要說幾句話。<br />\n<br />\n我不是要為 HA 撲火護航，我只是不吐不快。<br />\n現在，市民不滿、前線不滿、警察也不滿，這樣子的工作環境很難受。<br />\n<br />\n1、陳沛然議員指出的 AEIS 漏洞，的而且確，是存在已久的事實。所以，局方應該藉此機會與時並進，更新系統。<br />\n<strong><br />\n2、不過，如果是AEIS 集體洩密，在醫院的被捕病人理應會更多。有錯一定要改，但我認為由此洩密的可能性不高。<br />\n</strong><br />\n3、警察在金鐘集會被定性為騷亂/暴動後，在醫院大堂有特別留意有否「可疑」的病人來求診。<br />\n<strong><br />\n4、故此，我兩次發文「擦邊球」地提醒各位，在分流時要小心隔牆有耳。因為，由事件發生當晚開始，我就認為這是較大可能的原因。</strong><br />\n<br />\n5、前線同事需要自律，多加留意會否在和病人、或者和警察的對話當中，不慎透露了病人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n6、我相信同事們的專業道德，理應清楚知道醫護人員不能夠出賣病人對我們的信任。<br />\n人講你就信?<br />\n7、有警察指事件發生後，有同事指責他們是狗，叫他們用鼻嗅病人到哪去了。警方有就此正式向院方作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n8、無論是警察或是醫護，穿得起制服，就應當尊重自己的制服，約束言行，以免禍及整個團隊。<br />\n<br />\n9、在任何衝突中受傷的人，不論是市民、記者、還是警察，都應該能夠在公立醫院安心得到公平和合適的治療。<br />\n<br />\n10、例子：如果有一銀行劫匪受槍傷，或者黑社會份子受刀傷，自行來到醫院求醫，我會因為傷勢可疑，而問他是否需要報警。如果他拒絕或不能回應，我就不會主動報警。<br />\n<br />\n11、不過，如果我發現他身上有手槍或牛肉刀，那我就會立刻主動報警，因為涉及危害醫護人員和其他求診病人的安全，這就是可以唯一即場「篤灰」的理由。"},{"pid":"963efd9709f42c2bb9ac500227d1dc89c20456c6","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d386a218c413df1f240232d6184407ae5392f87b","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲講緊有人即時抄資料走人，你做乜撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"你抄俾我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳沛然當日係話HA乜架?<br />\n你又唔睇下DR RAY點認為?佢做開急症喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"1. 我駁你都費事，九唔搭八<br />\n2. 陳沛然係指HA當日點解容許有人抄到資料<br />\n<br />\n就憑你第一句&quot;你抄俾我睇下&quot;已經知你乜料啦"},{"pid":"450b6c4fa4d61a23c79c6ae87591727397b6c470","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"963efd9709f42c2bb9ac500227d1dc89c20456c6","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d386a218c413df1f240232d6184407ae5392f87b","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲講緊有人即時抄資料走人，你做乜撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"你抄俾我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳沛然當日係話HA乜架?<br />\n你又唔睇下DR RAY點認為?佢做開急症喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"1. 我駁你都費事，九唔搭八<br />\n2. 陳沛然係指HA當日點解容許有人抄到資料<br />\n<br />\n就憑你第一句&quot;你抄俾我睇下&quot;已經知你乜料啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/HA-police.html#more\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F06%2FHA-police.html%23more&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=078e1aac\" target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/HA-police.html#more</a><br />\n我真係駁你都費事<br />\n陳沛然自己一早收皮<br />\n3. 電腦系統問題 - (可信性 *****，可能性*)<br />\n<br />\n    3a) 醫管局電腦系統，我在記者會說明後，醫管局最終承認「急症室資訊系統」(AEIS) 有不需個人密碼登入，也有「警方」（For Police）字樣只是一個列印選項。<br />\n        我支持醫管局堵塞漏洞，盡力保護病人和求診的市民，員工必須透過個人密碼登入 AEIS；<br />\n        我接受醫管局的回應，在 AEIS 不會為警方查閱病人資訊而設的專用版面... 警方亦無權查閱。<br />\n    3b) 我質詢保安局局長及醫管局，關於警方的電腦系統 MIIDSS，再經調查後：<br />\n<br />\n        醫管局曾經在SARS 時候，將病人資料加密後傳送給警方 MIIDSS，再用人手輸入資料；<br />\n        經保安局局長及醫管局澄清指，現在醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統並沒有直接用實體線相連。<br />\n佢當日既指控<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/342421/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%AF%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80-%E7%84%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%B9%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F342421%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2580%25A3-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B9%25AB&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bky%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=12e11fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/342421/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E8%88%87%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%AF%E7%9B%B8%E9%80%A3-%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80-%E7%84%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%B9%AB</a><br />\n醫學界立法會議員陳沛然今天（19日）在立法會緊急質詢中稱，根據立法會文件及醫院管理局公開資料，醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統有一個程式是相連的，該系統為「重大事件調查及災難支援系統」，英文為「Major Incident Investigation and Disaster Support System」(MIIDSS)。<br />\n......<br />\n陳沛然前天（17日）披露，公立醫院急症室電腦有一個系統名為「AEIS」，設有警方專用版面，懷疑警員可透過系統獲得示威者的資料，從而作出拘捕，但醫院管理局當晚深夜面見傳媒，否認指控。<br />\n你弱智又好,唔識字又好,不如唔好上黎"},{"pid":"2c3bd53e2d5134358c1a3e10f7636d61d601284b","tid":1276808,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d386a218c413df1f240232d6184407ae5392f87b","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f","tid":1276808,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲講緊有人即時抄資料走人，你做乜撚？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"你抄俾我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳沛然當日係話HA乜架?<br />\n你又唔睇下DR RAY點認為?佢做開急症喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"電話相機影低得啦<br />\n真係攞簿仔鉛筆抄咩<br />\n定係個mon 有特別科技,影相會睇唔到"},{"pid":"aa92147bdb63a2121526520d226b8ca0499358dc","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2c3bd53e2d5134358c1a3e10f7636d61d601284b","tid":1276808,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d386a218c413df1f240232d6184407ae5392f87b","tid":1276808,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d794ef515bbb1c8d5ac3789907f227b3ffa3724f",